Working With The OpenActuUrlBundle as service
=============================================

Calling the service
-------------------

The call is simply done with "open-actu.url.manager"::

    <?php
    // app/AppKernel.php

    public function registerBundles()
    {
        $bundles = array(
            // ...
            new OpenActu\UrlBundle\OpenActuUrlBundle(),
            // ...
        );
    }

